Package com.uco.ucodgt.mvc.model.business.vehicle

Class VehicleDTO

java.lang.Object
com.uco.ucodgt.mvc.model.business.vehicle.VehicleDTO
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class VehicleDTO extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a vehicle in the system. This class encapsulates the data associated with a vehicle, including its license plate, type, color, ITV validity period, insurance ID, and insurance validity period.
